  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "You don't need a slash command. Claude Code Skills auto-trigger from your request.",
      "checksum": "sha256:099354f707aa9902a9661e26bf10ddb00278ae439536e96245e6649626d0136e",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here's how. A Skill is a SKILL dot M D file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:579cec4bafc989a9c64af1dc85763f1fe2fad6c710e287e723f1b502aa3a9831",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 13
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "It has a description plus instructions Claude follows.",
      "checksum": "sha256:54670bbc0a0a1fe6ed4bd490ea95a2a3996e10789059eac924eb0531f429da3b",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 24
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Auto-matching works on the description. Claude reads your request, compares it to all available skills, and activates the ones that match.",
      "checksum": "sha256:78d7ccf72df44e88c231958983967fd9a6a233baaff0fcb98b674ab394301140",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 7.198185941043084,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 32
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Slash commands and Skills are the same thing now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c9d0f64a02a098c7a2bb0df50b890d73a279b6ace40e08fa04c6b0f2a7fe359c",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 53
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Anthropic merged them. Both create the same command.",
      "checksum": "sha256:06e026792484b8816064901c6798ba497d34e0b7434a36b9c1197388697af506",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 62
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Supporting files keep the main skill focused. Templates, scripts, and reference docs live alongside.",
      "checksum": "sha256:993314b3c006e08698d66c2ed4a047ee67a06a753b29e3472fd0407d04cbb3c8",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 70
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Sharing depends on where you save it. Personal in your home directory.",
      "checksum": "sha256:763b2106b9c385309db470dd22f68ff368f8c32ced3f9a0cd4ca674667f05d3e",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 84
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Project in the repo. Team gets it via version control.",
      "checksum": "sha256:740a9e6b1b3b6015da66f56181a7cc96f793c40187372665f34732ab30cadf52",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 96
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Five real triggers. Say review this PR \u2014 pr-review fires.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a4dc064c227c0f34616670f6aaeca4dffc340685e6b4b727a1a738e021306bd9",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Say deploy to prod \u2014 deploy fires. Say commit my changes \u2014 commit fires.",
      "checksum": "sha256:059d7a029624fc1d2ec519ed14c5b47ac023e042bd4d7470d8afdb721c88d3ba",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 116
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Say add a feature \u2014 feature-spec fires. Say run the tests \u2014 test-runner fires.",
      "checksum": "sha256:72661239856d55d88a442c89488f8165e758851fef1f3da46b71c28d6c875ce1",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 130
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Watch the full breakdown for the rest of the customization system.",
      "checksum": "sha256:98248398596f300379147b38a7b6968c57fb708221c85c47e4419f1dd7ecb959",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
